Class Feedback

java.lang.Object
application.Feedback
public class Feedback extends Object
Represents feedback left by a student for a review.

    • Feedback

      public Feedback(String feedbackId, String reviewId, String studentUserName, int rating, String feedbackText, Timestamp createdAt)
      Create a Feedback instance.
      Parameters:
      feedbackId - unique id for the feedback
      reviewId - id of the review this feedback is about
      studentUserName - student who provided the feedback
      rating - numeric rating (0 if not used)
      feedbackText - optional free-text feedback
      createdAt - timestamp when feedback was created
